Rupia, who is now the league's top scorer with six goals, helped himself to a hat-trick to seal Leopards' third win of the season after a barren first half AFC Leopards striker Elvis Rupia was the star of the show as the hosts thrashed Sofapaka 3-0 in a BetKing Premier League match at Kasarani Annex on Saturday.
